{"tid":791988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【法律行動】梁振英今入稟控鍾劍華及立場新聞誹謗","createTime":"2018-08-24T08:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T11:14:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4544ef7d77236490efb740dcad925d183fc513","tid":791988,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席、前行政長官梁振英今日在社交網站發帖表示，其代表律師今天已入稟高等法院，控告理工大學應用社會科學系助理教授鍾劍華及網上媒體《立場新聞》誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n梁振英強調，香港人有言論和新聞自由，同時所有人都有免於被誹謗的權利，這種權利受民事和刑事法的保護，罔顧事實中傷他人的人應該受到法律制裁。梁振英同時表示，早前發給兩被告的律師信已經上載在律師行的網頁：<a href=\"http://www.sfks.com.hk/tc/profile/ournews_details.php?id=271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfks.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fprofile%2Fournews_details.php%3Fid%3D271&d=eW0Sk9Fb8fg7W5dzKqi%2FD2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=ac9a9ccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sfks.com.hk/tc/profile/ournews_details.php?id=271</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》是於日前刊登鍾劍華的文章，有意無意間將梁振英與黑社會拉上關係。該篇題為「五年前的這件事與梁振英的紅線論」的文章是於本月初刊登，文中提到「江湖人物拖馬撐梁振英」，又質疑梁振英「與黑社會或江湖中人有甚麼關係」等。文章配以2013年《主場新聞》製圖，設計圖片中的「梁振英」身穿白色背心，胸部有紋身，暗示梁振英與黑社會有關，涉惡意指控及誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/37240/-%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E6%8E%A7%E9%8D%BE%E5%8A%8D%E8%8F%AF%E5%8F%8A%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F37240%2F-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%258A%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%25AA%25B9%25E8%25AC%2597&d=eW0Sk9Fb8fg7W5dzKqi%2FD2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=b739e181\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/37240/-%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E4%BB%8A%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E6%8E%A7%E9%8D%BE%E5%8A%8D%E8%8F%AF%E5%8F%8A%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%AA%B9%E8%AC%97</a>"},{"pid":"156776a10f94281a5f81c35120105acd47e8e1ba","tid":791988,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"雖軟必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ff205d58b8c1eedef38005fb71719241ed6605","tid":791988,"uid":18385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"岩岩輸左場特事特辦，要搵野補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b81392c3dcdcf054676e381ffaa8025b4804488","tid":791988,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"輸間廠，贏條毛，唔告正契弟"},{"pid":"12642b6c81a4fa839d1b80611fa028b76872fd94","tid":791988,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56ff205d58b8c1eedef38005fb71719241ed6605","tid":791988,"uid":18385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"岩岩輸左場特事特辦，要搵野補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"仲可以上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbca85b33b148db785ca2eb51d349d7a380e3da","tid":791988,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"佢上年七一比大內總管栗戰書趕落機<br />\n至今仍為人津津樂道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}